---
// src/components/GrowthEngine.astro
---
<section id="tech" class="py-24 bg-slate-900 relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 w-full h-full overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-full bg-[url('/grid.svg')] opacity-[0.05]"></div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/4 left-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-blue-600/20 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 right-1/4 w-[500px] h-[500px] bg-cyan-500/10 rounded-full blur-[120px]"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
        
        <div class="text-center max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-20">
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-6 tracking-tight text-display">
                The "Digital Franchise" Model.
            </h2>
            <p class="text-slate-400 text-lg md:text-xl font-light leading-relaxed">
                Most websites are like a single flyer. Stegg is a printing press that creates a custom, highly-relevant landing page for every single neighborhood you serve.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mb-24">
            <div class="bg-slate-800/50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-red-500/20 relative overflow-hidden">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10">
                    <i data-lucide="frown" class="w-24 h-24 text-red-500"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-red-500"></span>
                    Standard Website
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-400">
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Fights for generic keywords like "Renovation Malaysia" (Too competitive).</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Requires expensive Google Ads to get traffic.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="x" class="w-5 h-5 text-red-500 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span>Generic content doesn't convince local buyers.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-900/50 to-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-blue-500/50 relative overflow-hidden shadow-2xl shadow-blue-900/20">
                <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 p-4 opacity-10">
                    <i data-lucide="trophy" class="w-24 h-24 text-blue-400"></i>
                </div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                    <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-400 animate-pulse"></span>
                    Stegg Growth Engine
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4 text-slate-300">
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>Dominates local keywords</strong> like "Renovation Shah Alam" (High intent).</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>Zero Ad Spend:</strong> Organic traffic from 50+ locations.</span>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex gap-3">
                        <i data-lucide="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-blue-400 shrink-0"></i>
                        <span><strong>Hyper-Relevant:</strong> Customers see their city name and trust you instantly.</span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto">
            <div class="text-center mb-10">
                <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-xs uppercase tracking-widest bg-blue-900/30 px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-blue-500/30">
                    Live Simulation
                </span>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mt-4">See how Google sees your business.</h3>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-2xl border border-slate-700 ring-4 ring-slate-800">
                <div class="bg-slate-800 px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-4 border-b border-slate-700">
                    <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/50"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/50"></div>
                        <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/50"></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 bg-slate-950/50 rounded-md text-center py-1.5 text-xs font-mono text-slate-500 flex justify-center items-center gap-2">
                        <i data-lucide="lock" class="w-3 h-3"></i> google.com/search
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 divide-y md:divide-y-0 md:divide-x divide-slate-700">
                    
                    <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-slate-50/10 transition-colors">
                        <div class="mb-8 relative">
                            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">Customer in Shah Alam types:</span>
                            <div class="bg-white rounded-full h-12 flex items-center px-5 shadow-lg relative z-10">
                                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-3"><i data-lucide="search" class="w-4 h-4"></i></span>
                                <span class="text-slate-800 text-sm font-medium">Renovation contractor <span class="text-blue-600">Shah Alam</span></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="layers" class="w-3 h-3 text-slate-600"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col">
                                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-800 font-bold leading-none">Stegg.</span>
                                    <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-none">stegg.co › renovation-shah-alam</span>
                                </div>
                                <i data-lucide="more-vertical" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 ml-auto"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="text-[#1a0dab] text-lg font-medium hover:underline cursor-pointer leading-tight mb-1">
                                Top Rated Renovation in Shah Alam | Free Quote
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Looking for renovation in <strong>Shah Alam</strong>? We specialize in terrace houses in Section 7, Glenmarie & Setia Alam. 100% On-time completion...
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div class="p-8 bg-slate-50/5 relative overflow-hidden group hover:bg-slate-50/10 transition-colors">
                         <div class="mb-8 relative">
                            <span class="text-[10px] font-bold text-slate-500 uppercase tracking-wider mb-2 block">Customer in Cyberjaya types:</span>
                            <div class="bg-white rounded-full h-12 flex items-center px-5 shadow-lg relative z-10">
                                <span class="text-slate-400 mr-3"><i data-lucide="search" class="w-4 h-4"></i></span>
                                <span class="text-slate-800 text-sm font-medium">Renovation contractor <span class="text-cyan-600">Cyberjaya</span></span>
                            </div>
                        </div>

                        <div class="bg-white p-4 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-slate-200">
                            <div class="flex items-center gap-2 mb-1">
                                <div class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-100 flex items-center justify-center">
                                    <i data-lucide="layers" class="w-3 h-3 text-slate-600"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="flex flex-col">
                                    <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-800 font-bold leading-none">Stegg.</span>
                                    <span class="text-[9px] text-slate-500 leading-none">stegg.co › renovation-cyberjaya</span>
                                </div>
                                <i data-lucide="more-vertical" class="w-4 h-4 text-slate-400 ml-auto"></i>
                            </div>
                            <h4 class="text-[#1a0dab] text-lg font-medium hover:underline cursor-pointer leading-tight mb-1">
                                Modern Office & Home Renovation Cyberjaya
                            </h4>
                            <p class="text-xs text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">
                                Expert renovation services for <strong>Cyberjaya</strong> tech offices and condos. Smart home integration available. Book a consultation today...
                            </p>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-center text-slate-500 mt-8 text-sm">
                *The Growth Engine generates these distinct, highly-ranking pages automatically.
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>
</section>